Name:         African Wild Dog
Scientific:   Lycaon pictus
Class:        Mammalia
Habitat:      Savanna
Diet:         Carnivore
Lifespan:     11 years
Weight:       30 kg
Status:       Endangered
Fact:         80% hunting success rate; votes on hunts by sneezing democratically

Name:         Snow Leopard
Scientific:   Panthera uncia
Class:        Mammalia
Habitat:      Mountain
Diet:         Carnivore
Lifespan:     15 years
Weight:       55 kg
Status:       Vulnerable
Fact:         Cannot roar; uses long tail as blanket; leaps 15 meters

Name:         Cheetah
Scientific:   Acinonyx jubatus
Class:        Mammalia
Habitat:      Savanna
Diet:         Carnivore
